{"_id":"post-9ee0a4f3-eadd-4151-bcf2-8b6ee7804b5a","_type":"post","title":"A database for every repl","slug":{"_type":"slug","current":"database"},"body":[{"_key":"42390ae8059e","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Repl.it is already the best place to build your apps. But there was a missing piece: where do you store your data?","_key":"42390ae8059e0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"ca67969a4e48","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"We’re introducing Repl.it Database: a fast, free, and easy key-value store that’s built into every repl.[](preview end)","_key":"ca67969a4e480"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"688a12194c82","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"All you have to do is import one of our packages for ","_key":"688a12194c820"},{"_type":"span","marks":["64091a1cf92e"],"text":"Python","_key":"688a12194c821"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":", ","_key":"688a12194c822"},{"_type":"span","marks":["2987ccbfc7d1"],"text":"Node.js","_key":"688a12194c823"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":", or ","_key":"688a12194c824"},{"_type":"span","marks":["f7e5223a4dc5"],"text":"Go","_key":"688a12194c825"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":", and you can instantly start setting keys in your database.","_key":"688a12194c826"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"64091a1cf92e","_type":"link","href":"https://pypi.org/project/replit/"},{"_key":"2987ccbfc7d1","_type":"link","href":"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@replit/database"},{"_key":"f7e5223a4dc5","_type":"link","href":"https://github.com/replit/database-go"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"fc380144e0a6","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"fc380144e0a60","text":"","marks":[]}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"ecf94ad5293e","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Because Database is built-in, there is no setup, provisioning, or configuration. It's the fastest and easiest way to store data on Repl.it.","_key":"ecf94ad5293e0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"1bd77a2fcd48","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"To get off the ground, fork our ","_key":"1bd77a2fcd480"},{"_type":"span","marks":["ccbf2b4c24cb"],"text":"example Python and Flask emoji app","_key":"1bd77a2fcd481"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" so that you can quickly get to hacking!","_key":"1bd77a2fcd482"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"ccbf2b4c24cb","_type":"link","href":"https://repl.it/@util/Database-Flask-comments-example"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_type":"embed","_id":"9b060af3-fdd2-489c-8401-4f424442fee1","url":"https://repl.it/@util/Database-Flask-emoji-example?embed=true","_key":"ea7c5f4bba94"},{"_key":"0e25e1546d23","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Key-value","_key":"0e25e1546d230"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"h2"},{"_key":"46c89524b4e7","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Key-value databases are conceptually simple: they’re a flat map of keys to their values. There are no schemas, tables, or columns. There are only a few operations that you need to perform: set a key to a value, get a key’s value, delete a key, and search for keys.","_key":"46c89524b4e70"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"fc767ef3249e","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Those simple operations are enough to support all kinds of applications, from blogs with posts and comments, to game backends with leaderboards, to ","_key":"fc767ef3249e0"},{"_type":"span","marks":["4cdccfba665d"],"text":"email platforms","_key":"fc767ef3249e1"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":".","_key":"fc767ef3249e2"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"4cdccfba665d","_type":"link","href":"https://repl.email"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"93cd1c7ca7a4","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Multi-language","_key":"93cd1c7ca7a40"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"h2"},{"_key":"850fe81e33ad","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"We provide Database clients for ","_key":"850fe81e33ad0"},{"_type":"span","marks":["04ba3509ff8e"],"text":"Python","_key":"850fe81e33ad1"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":", ","_key":"850fe81e33ad2"},{"_type":"span","marks":["e7474e320c3b"],"text":"Node.js","_key":"850fe81e33ad3"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":", or ","_key":"850fe81e33ad4"},{"_type":"span","marks":["bfa66b2b7d47"],"text":"Go","_key":"850fe81e33ad5"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":". But you can talk to Database from any language over HTTP. Take a look at ","_key":"850fe81e33ad6"},{"_type":"span","marks":["1b63cc265db4"],"text":"the documentation","_key":"850fe81e33ad7"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" for more details.","_key":"850fe81e33ad8"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"04ba3509ff8e","_type":"link","href":"https://pypi.org/project/replit/"},{"_key":"e7474e320c3b","_type":"link","href":"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@replit/database"},{"_key":"bfa66b2b7d47","_type":"link","href":"https://github.com/replit/database-go"},{"_key":"1b63cc265db4","_type":"link","href":"https://docs.repl.it/misc/database"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"dc824b9a5770","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"In Python, our client serializes and deserializes dictionaries and lists so that you can use them to store more complex data:","_key":"dc824b9a57700"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"f7fbda13fcdc","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"f7fbda13fcdc0","text":"","marks":[]}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"4d14725951b6","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Get started","_key":"4d14725951b60"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"h2"},{"_key":"105f93878889","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Repl.it is the best place to start building your app. And Database is the easiest way to just jump in, get coding, and store your data without having to set anything up.","_key":"105f938788890"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"0f4f601b1d9d","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"For more details on Database, click on the Database icon in your repl’s sidebar or ","_key":"0f4f601b1d9d0"},{"_type":"span","marks":["6cb56a4a736b"],"text":"check out the documentation","_key":"0f4f601b1d9d1"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":".","_key":"0f4f601b1d9d2"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"6cb56a4a736b","_type":"link","href":"https://docs.repl.it/misc/database"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"3d36183749cd","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"With Database, you can build a fully-featured app entirely on Repl.it. We can’t wait to see what you create!","_key":"3d36183749cd0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"}],"publishedAt":"2020-09-14T00:00:00.000Z"}